If you like Pina Colada…..🍍🥥🍹🌞 #cleanpartner

Tropical Escape by @cleanclassicperfume is literally a summer cocktail in a bottle—juicy pineapple, creamy coconut, and soft sandalwood that instantly transports you to golden hour on an island somewhere, cocktail in hand (minus the hangover) 🥴

It’s totally dreamy. If warm, beachy scents are your thing, you’re going to be obsessed.

FRAGRANCE NOTES
🍍 Top: Pineapple, Bergamot, Orange
🥥 Mid: Coconut Milk, Heliotrope, Jasmine
🍹 Dry: Sandalwood, Cedarwood, Tonka Bean

Available at @ultabeauty and cleanbeauty.com

#cleanbeauty #ulta #cleanclassic #tropicalescape #sotd

Beach Blossom Cologne ☀️🍋‍🟩🥥🤍 Kindly gifted by Jo Malone London

This not your typical beachy summer scent, it’s light, fresh and very elegant.  I also love the beautiful design of the bottle and how the glass shifts from golden amber to clear depending on the light. 

🍋‍🟩Top Note ~ Lime
🥥 Heart Note ~ Coconut Water
🤍 Base Note ~ Tonka Bean

Its exclusively available at @sephora

latestPosts.caption:
Strawberry Fields 🍓🌸✨ the newest fragrance from @cleanclassicperfume #CLEANPARTNER 

If you love a fruity floral that’s crisp, clean, and effortlessly pretty, this one’s for you. Inspired by juicy, wild strawberries sparkling under the morning sun, it’s fresh and slightly sweet, while jasmine petals and orchid blossoms add a soft femininity. Finally, the white musk and amber create a warm, skin-like finish. 

FRAGRANCE NOTES: 
🍓Top: Wild Strawberry, Linen Accord 
🌸Mid: Jasmine Petals, Orchid Blossom 
🤍Dry: White Musk, Amber 

Such a pretty clean girl scent! You can find it at @ultabeauty @macys and cleanbeauty.com 

#cleanclassic #strawberryfields #strawberrygirl #strawberryseason #aesthetic #cleangirlaesthetic #fragrancelover #sotd #asmr #aesthetically #cleanfragrance

Whipped cherry 🍒🧁✨ #cleanpartner 

Cherry definitely had its moment in 2024, and it’s finishing on a high with CLEAN RESERVE Whipped Cherry the newest release by @Cleanbeauty_collective. 
Yummy, delicious, and beautifully balanced, this fragrance is everything you’d want in a cherry scent. The blend of juicy fruits, delicious cream, delicate florals, and calming musk feels effortless—not too sweet and not too heavy just a soft, creamy blend that feels sophisticated yet playful. It’s the ultimate cherry on top of your fragrance collection and absolutely worth a trip to @Sephora to sniff. 

The notes
TOP: Wild Cherry, Pineapple, Coconut Water, Orange Zest�
MID: Almond Blossom, Praline, Mimosa, Osmanthus 
DRY: Vanilla Cream, Cedarwood, Musk, Sandalwood
